[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/76/287622.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1374576","time":"2018-8-14 22:12","userId":"trim21","userName":"Trim21","userSign":"(异端比异教徒更可恨)","message":"闭眼是本能 等死不是吧…<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/71/227195.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1374584","time":"2018-8-14 22:34","userId":"227195","userName":"thofoofintwsi","userSign":"","message":"不会得救，详见赌博默示录最后部分，<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">开司断手指。</span><br>我觉得人的本能应该是求生，闭眼等死应该是遇到刺激太大了，太紧张不知道怎么反应了。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/76/7650.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1374585","time":"2018-8-14 22:39","userId":"iiiiuuuu","userName":"完全没有","userSign":"(就是没有)","message":"女主是，男主不是","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1374592","time":"2018-8-14 23:16","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"诚哥没闭眼不还是…"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/55/175549.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1374590","time":"2018-8-14 23:10","userId":"blue956650063","userName":"「 」","userSign":"(飛べ。)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">是的，以前也想过这个问题。为什么遇到危险时要闭上眼愣在那里啊，赶紧跑才对啊。<br>后来想想应该是生物的那种本能……？可能就是被吓到了然后动不了了吧。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/60/146072.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1374599","time":"2018-8-14 23:49","userId":"hottomper","userName":"绯红の空","userSign":"","message":"愣在那里就是战或逃的本能反应啊。。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1374593","time":"2018-8-14 23:23","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"什么样的生命危险? 如果是躲不开的拳头之类的 闭眼的本能是为了保护双眼, 让更硬的头骨承受冲击..并不是在等死 反而是在求生..<br>至于动画..其实我一直觉得那些片段都挺违和的..正确做法应该是闭眼抱头蹲下/后退..会不会是因为懒得画那么多动作<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1374595","time":"2018-8-14 23:30","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"","message":"扑上来的怪兽，飞过来的攻击，劈下来的刀剑之类的"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1374598","time":"2018-8-14 23:47","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">君寻</span> 说: 扑上来的怪兽，飞过来的攻击，劈下来的刀剑之类的</q></div>那就是我说的[躲不开的拳头]之类的了..躲不开时闭上眼然后用手护住自己并且尽量躲开都是人的本能..<br>所以我觉得动画应该是取材自这种动作.. 闭眼→被救 的发生速度是很快的 应该是想表达[千钧一发时被救]的意思吧..只是动画没有表现得很好..闭眼到被救的时间太长, 就好像在等死一样.."}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/36/313629.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1374604","time":"2018-8-15 00:17","userId":"dusk_raven","userName":"Dusk_Raven","userSign":"(では、 あなたは何故、ココにいるの？ ... ... ... ... ...)","message":"有时候反应不过来吧。之前遇到过一个酒驾的车祸，侧面撞过来的，受害人即便是看到了，也只是抬了抬手象征性地挡了一下，双腿已经迈不开了。<br>动画里主要是对面攻速太慢导致观众感觉受害人在闭眼等死。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/35/273543.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1374607","time":"2018-8-15 00:29","userId":"hydrilla","userName":"黑藻","userSign":"(黑藻并非藻类！)","message":"比如要被男主亲上的时候？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/05/310594.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1374609","time":"2018-8-15 00:31","userId":"tmpfs","userName":"​","userSign":"","message":"闭眼的确是等死。在本能的层面上死不可怕，痛是可怕的。<br><br>It is easier to find men who will volunteer to die, than to find those who are willing to endure pain with patience. - Julius Caesar","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1374610","time":"2018-8-15 00:50","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"刀子劈过来也很痛啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211998.jpg","floor":"#9-2","id":"1374689","time":"2018-8-15 22:56","userId":"211998","userName":"秘则为花","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Cedar</span> 说: 刀子劈过来也很痛啊</q></div>所以达官贵人就是鸩酒或者三尺白绫，逆党反贼就是五马分尸或者凌迟处死。总之，观看处刑仪式就是要让观看者感受到身体的折磨和疼痛。看着疼。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/89/328933.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1374628","time":"2018-8-15 10:00","userId":"tohka","userName":"Tohka","userSign":"(爱老婆，爱十香)","message":"还是混吃等死比较好","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1374629","time":"2018-8-15 10:05","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"(V1046-R MAHORO)","message":"为啥拿动画做论据……","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/84/268422.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1374638","time":"2018-8-15 13:19","userId":"alexio_yorbmapr","userName":"海盗丸子","userSign":"","message":"同问"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#11-2","id":"1374639","time":"2018-8-15 13:45","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"","message":"因为只在动画里才有啊"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#11-3","id":"1374724","time":"2018-8-16 04:39","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">君寻</span> 说: 因为只在动画里才有啊</q></div>啥意思，现实中人也遇到过生命危险啊"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#11-4","id":"1374739","time":"2018-8-16 08:44","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: 啥意思，现实中人也遇到过生命危险啊</q></div>有相关的记录视频吗？"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/15/20/152017.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1374723","time":"2018-8-16 03:28","userId":"leon92101","userName":"御户白夜","userSign":"(深層「無意識の遺伝子」)","message":"Dylan said it first and best:\"he not busy being born, is busy dying.\"","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/78/307891.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1374737","time":"2018-8-16 08:28","userId":"307891","userName":"川水","userSign":"(Anime is a gag, and so are its dilettantes.)","message":"心理恐惧=闭眼<br>没有活路=愣住<br>生理惊吓=蜷缩身体<br><br>影视里的闭眼等死那是觉悟了。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/99/139922.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"13